      "text": "私と琴乃ちゃんとの出会いは中学生になった頃\n私達は一年生の時、同じクラスだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono and I met in middle school.\nOur first year of middle school‚ we were in the same class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃の琴乃ちゃんは、ずっと不機嫌そうにしていて\nクラスの中で孤立したみたいになっていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ Kotono always looked like she was in a bad mood.\nShe sort of became the lone wolf in class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.633333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 15.931111240386997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が中学に入った頃だと\nちょうど私に仕事が入り始めた時期かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The year Kotono started middle school…\nthat was right around the time I started work as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5644445737203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 21.831111240387003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃と過ごす時間がどんどんなくなっちゃって\nいつの間にか、あの子とすれ違うようになってた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’d spend less and less time together‚\nuntil‚ before I realized it‚ we’d almost become strangers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.843301677703863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 28.78580503463741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "私も初めは怖い子なのかなって思ってたんですけど\nちょっと寂しそうにしてるところを見ちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I thought Kotono was intimidating‚\nbut I caught a glimpse of her once‚ looking a little sad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.18580503463744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 36.019138367970776
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それで琴乃ちゃんのことが気になってたある日\n琴乃ちゃんが教室に置き忘れたノートを発見したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I started noticing Kotono a little more‚ one day‚\nI spotted a notebook Kotono had forgotten in the classroom.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.68580503463743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "好奇心に負けてノートを開くと――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Out of curiosity‚ I opened the notebook and…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.38580503463744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 46.849909448623606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
