      "text": "（こうして正直に答える素直さも魅力的な）\n（個性なんだけどな……いや、今は黙って聞こう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I think the honest way she’s expressing her feelings is charming.)\n(That makes her unique enough… but I’ll stay quiet and keep listening.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.03603187402089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.810929799079894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
