      "text": "普段の人を寄せつけない孤高な雰囲気とは全然違う\n可愛くてファンシーなイラストが描かれていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her notebook showed a girl completely unlike the intimidating loner I knew.\nIt was full of cute‚ girlish drawings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.57759646574657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、それはどれも、二人の女の子が\n楽しそうに手を繋いでいるものばかりでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s more‚ all of the drawings were of two girls‚\nsmiling and holding hands.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.44426313241325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 74.67759646574662
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "それは、全くの想像だったのかもしれないし\nクラスの誰かだったのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those girls might have been entirely made-up‚\nand they might have been people in our class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.67759646574659,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
