      "text": "ともかく私はそれを見て、以前に見かけた寂しげな顔は\n見間違いじゃなかったんだと思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But anyway‚ when I saw those drawings and thought back to her sad smile earlier‚\nI realized my eyes weren’t mistaken back then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたらそこに息を切らせた琴乃ちゃんが来て\n私はノートを開いているところを見られちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ Kotono ran into the room‚ short of breath‚\nand she caught me looking at her notebook.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 101
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
