      "text": "それはもう……一生懸命に謝ったんですけど\nなかなか許してはくれませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ boy‚ did she ever… I apologized over and over again‚\nbut she wouldn’t forgive me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 110.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "でも、絶対に友達になりたかったから\n諦めずに謝りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I definitely wanted to be her friend‚\nso I never gave up apologizing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "何度無視されても、めげずに声をかけたりして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how many times she ignored me‚ I kept trying to talk to her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 120.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "どうしてそんなに友達になりたかったんだ？\n本当は寂しがり屋なのかも、って思っただけなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why were you that desperate to become her friend?\nWas it really only because you thought she was secretly lonely?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "それもあるんですけど、本当の理由は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that was part of it. But the real reason was…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
