      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、私がノートを開いてることに気づいて\n顔を真っ赤にして恥ずかしそうにしたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because when Kotono caught me looking at her notebook‚\nshe blushed bright red in embarrassment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
