    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "一瞬だけだったんですけど\nそれでなんかキュゥンって来ちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was just for a moment‚\nbut it really tugged on my heartstrings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "絶対にこの子と仲良くなりたい\nって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I knew I just had to be her friend.\nI knew it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 146.33333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "……渚ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.33333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 147.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それですっかり琴乃に惚れ込んでしまった\nということ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you fell head over heels in love with Kotono.\nIs that right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。最初のきっかけはそうです\nでも話すようになって、ますます好きになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I guess it was an infatuation at first.\nBut after I got to talk to her‚ I liked her even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 160.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "実はすっごく友達想いな子なんだってわかったのも\n琴乃ちゃんと友達付き合いできるようになってからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I learned just how thoughtful and generous she is as a friend.\nThat happened after we became friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "壁を作っちゃうことが多いのは、想いが深すぎて\n人数の許容量が少ないからなんじゃないかって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I learned that maybe the reason why she often put up walls\nwas because she’d get overly invested in the few people she let in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 175.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs023.m4a",
      "text": "だからこそ、大好きだった麻奈さんが亡くなった時は\n目も当てられない状態になっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which was why when Mana‚ her beloved sister‚ passed away‚\nshe was in such a terrible state.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 182.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
