      "text": "これだと思ったことに真正面から取り組める\n自分に正直でストレートなところもすごいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When she knows what she wants‚ she just goes for it‚ head-on.\nShe’s honest with herself and with others‚ and that’s amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs025.m4a",
      "text": "本気で取り組む琴乃ちゃんを見てると\nそれだけでぐっと引き込まれるものがあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whenever I watch Kotono‚ really going for something‚\nI’m just drawn in by that quality of hers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 196.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs026.m4a",
      "text": "あれはきっと天性のカリスマ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet that’s her natural charisma.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs027.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんはアイドルとして\n最強の武器を持っていると思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think Kotono has\nthe perfect weapon as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.66666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 204.16666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs028.m4a",
      "text": "それからやっぱりダンスの才能も凄いですよね\n例えば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ she’s got an amazing talent for dancing.\nFor example—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "待った、待った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold it right there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 211.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、なんで止めちゃうの？\nもう少し聞かせてもらっても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Why are you stopping her?\nI wouldn’t mind hearing a little more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
