      "startTime": 214.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 215.83333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "渚が琴乃のことを大好きだということは\nよく分かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ Nagisa. You love Kotono.\nThat’s very clear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs029.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すみません\n私の個性を考えようというお話でしたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… Sorry.\nI was supposed to be thinking about what makes me unique.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 225.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs030.m4a",
      "text": "私はそんな琴乃ちゃんの『個性』に\n憧れてきたんだと思うんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that Kotono’s uniqueness\nhas been something I’ve aspired to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs031.m4a",
      "text": "それは私にはないもの……\nだから私は琴乃ちゃんを支えたいと思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s something that I don’t have.\nThat’s why I wanted to support Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 236.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs032.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの傍で、その夢を実現させるための\nお手伝いがしたいと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to stay by her side and help make her dreams come true.\nI wanted to be the one who helped her do that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それで星見プロに、か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And that’s why you joined Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 246.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs033.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実際にデビューしてみたら\n誰かのお手伝いだけじゃダメだって気がついて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But once I actually made my debut‚\nI realized that just helping someone else wasn’t good enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs034.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前ですよね……\nお客さんにとっては私もアイドルの一人",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course it isn’t.\nTo the audience‚ I’m another idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 258.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs035.m4a",
      "text": "そう思ってくれるお客さんをちゃんと喜ばせないと\nアイドルとは言えないんじゃないか……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If they see me as an idol‚ I have to bring them joy.\nOtherwise‚ I can’t call myself a proper idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.26666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 265.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03/sud_vo_adv_main_01_06_03-ngs036.m4a",
      "text": "私はずっと琴乃ちゃんのことだけを考えてきて\n自分のことを考えてこなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve come all this way thinking only of Kotono.\nI wasn’t thinking about myself at all.",
